<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="id"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Contoh Pengisian Target - <%= appName %></title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css"></head><body class="mp-public-body"><header class="mp-navbar"><a class="mp-brand" href="/"><span class="mp-brand-logo">M</span><span><%= appName %></span></a><nav class="mp-nav-menu"><a href="/services">Layanan</a><a href="/faq">FAQ</a><a href="/login" class="mp-nav-login">Masuk</a></nav></header><main class="mp-page-main"><section class="mp-page-hero"><span class="mp-eyebrow">Panduan Target</span><h1>Contoh Pengisian Target</h1><p>Gunakan format target yang benar agar order tidak gagal, partial, atau delay.</p></section><div class="table-card"><table><thead><tr><th>Platform</th><th>Jenis Layanan</th><th>Format</th><th>Contoh</th><th>Catatan</th></tr></thead><tbody><% examples.forEach(item=>{ %><tr><td><%= item.platform %></td><td><%= item.service_type %></td><td><%= item.target_format %></td><td><code><%= item.example %></code></td><td><%= item.note || '-' %></td></tr><% }) %></tbody></table></div></main></body></html>